<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Account Deleted - Source Build</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            background-color: #f7f7f7;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ef4444 0%, #dc2626 100%);
            color: #ffffff;
            padding: 40px 30px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .header h1 {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: 600;
        }
        .content {
            padding: 40px 30px;
        }
        .content h2 {
            color: #ef4444;
            font-size: 22px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .content p {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            color: #555;
            line-height: 1.8;
        }
        .alert-box {
            background-color: #fee2e2;
            border-left: 4px solid #ef4444;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 30px 0;
            border-radius: 4px;
        }
        .alert-box h3 {
            color: #dc2626;
            margin-top: 0;
            font-size: 18px;
        }
        .alert-box p {
            margin: 10px 0;
            color: #666;
        }
        .info-section {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 30px 0;
        }
        .info-section h3 {
            color: #333;
            font-size: 18px;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }
        .info-section p {
            color: #555;
            margin: 10px 0;
        }
        .data-retention {
            background-color: #fefce8;
            border: 1px solid #fde047;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .data-retention h4 {
            color: #713f12;
            margin-top: 0;
            font-size: 16px;
        }
        .data-retention ul {
            list-style: none;
            padding: 0;
            margin: 0;
            color: #555;
        }
        .data-retention li {
            padding: 5px 0;
        }
        .cta-button {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: #6b7280;
            color: #ffffff;
            text-decoration: none;
            padding: 12px 30px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 16px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .cta-button:hover {
            background-color: #4b5563;
        }
        .footer {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 30px;
            text-align: center;
            color: #666;
            font-size: 14px;
            border-top: 1px solid #e9ecef;
        }
        .footer a {
            color: #6b7280;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        .footer a:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }
        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            .container {
                width: 100%;
            }
            .header, .content, .footer {
                padding: 20px;
            }
            .header h1 {
                font-size: 24px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>Account Deletion Confirmation</h1>
        </div>
        
        <div class="content">
            <h2>Hello <%= name %>,</h2>
            
            <p>
                We're writing to confirm that your Source Build account has been <strong>permanently deleted</strong> from our system.
            </p>
            
            <div class="alert-box">
                <h3>Account Details:</h3>
                <p><strong>Email:</strong> <%= email %></p>
                <p><strong>Account Type:</strong> <%= accountType %></p>
                <p><strong>Deletion Date:</strong> <%= date %></p>
                <% if (reason) { %>
                <p><strong>Reason:</strong> <%= reason %></p>
                <% } %>
            </div>
            
            <div class="info-section">
                <h3>What This Means:</h3>
                <p>Your account and associated data have been removed from Source Build. This includes:</p>
                <ul style="color: #555; margin-left: 20px;">
                    <li>• Your profile information and settings</li>
                    <li>• Order history and transaction records</li>
                    <li>• Messages and communications</li>
                    <li>• Saved preferences and favorites</li>
                    <li>• Any active listings or services</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            
            <div class="data-retention">
                <h4>⚠️ Important Information About Data Retention</h4>
                <ul>
                    <li>• Some data may be retained for legal and compliance purposes</li>
                    <li>• Transaction records may be kept for tax and accounting requirements</li>
                    <li>• This deletion is permanent and cannot be reversed</li>
                    <li>• You will need to create a new account if you wish to use Source Build in the future</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            
            <h3>Need Help?</h3>
            
            <p>
                If this deletion was not initiated by you or if you believe this was done in error, please contact our support team immediately:
            </p>
            
            <div style="text-align: center;">
                <a href="mailto:<%= supportEmail %>" class="cta-button">Contact Support</a>
            </div>
            
            <p>
                We're sorry to see you go. If you have any feedback about your experience with Source Build that you'd like to share, we'd appreciate hearing from you.
            </p>
            
            <p>
                Thank you for being part of the Source Build community.
            </p>
            
            <p style="margin-top: 30px;">
                Best regards,<br>
                <strong>The Source Build Team</strong>
            </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="footer">
            <p>
                This email was sent to <%= email %><br>
                You received this email to confirm the deletion of your Source Build account.
            </p>
            
            <p style="margin-top: 20px; font-size: 12px;">
                This is a system-generated notification. Your account has been deleted and you will not receive further emails from Source Build unless you create a new account.
            </p>
            
            <p style="margin-top: 20px;">
                © <%= year %> Source Build. All rights reserved.<br>
                <a href="<%= privacyUrl %>">Privacy Policy</a> | 
                <a href="<%= termsUrl %>">Terms of Service</a>
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>